        <abstract>
            <p>Admires DO’s correlation of spiny tree species and dry hot climate. CD suggests that spines, like strange aroma of desert plants, protect against browsing where there are few plants.</p>
            <p>Fragrance and unisexuality.</p> 
<p>Dimorphism in <hi rend="italic">Viola tricolor</hi>.</p> 
